snippet.title: Katrina insists that she did not tamper with the DNA Test | Nang Ngumiti Ang Langit
snippet.description:
Britney (Heart Ramos) overhears Katrina (Cristine Reyes) confronting Michael (RK Bagatsing) for doubting her claim that Amber (Krystal Mejes) is his daughter. (With English Subtitles)
